name: Field Promotion (V)
Lore: 'Imperial officers are fiercely competitive, especially on the Executor. Lord Vader''s flagship is a place where devious political calculation prospers. The naive are doomed to failure.',
Text: 'Deploy on your captain or commander. This character is an admiral and a leader. Imperials are immune to Demotion. Once per game, may take a card with ''Imperial'' in title into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)',
